nodes.text: And wouldn't it be great that rather than giving the same old canned responses that are based in the same old false assumptions, and the mocking insults toward me, that your side actually dealt with the questions asked. Only then, with objective and serious consideration will you evos realize how you have been duped by scientific gibberish and pseudo intellectual psycho babble that lead very simple people into thinking that with such big words and so scientific a vocabulary, the lie of evo must be at least based in truth. I submit to you that nothing could be further from the truth.
I think there are few better things than self-evident irony. I love it. :)
